				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ff4a814 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="ff4a814" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Panda JR</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f6a9544 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="f6a9544" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>The Panda Print and Apply Label Applicator is designed to automatically print and apply self-adhesive labels in real time efficiently and reliably. It is well proven in a variety of variable data printing applications, including logistics and tote labelling, to primary product ready meals and fresh produce labelling. Thanks to its incredibly robust deign the Panda is capable of operating in the harshest industrial environments.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Electronic Control :</strong> ER</li><li><strong>Display :</strong> 4 LED &#8211; Function Keys</li><li><strong>Print Engine :</strong> Sato® LT408 – 4″ (105mm)</li><li><strong>Applicator Unit :</strong> Pneumatic Linear</li><li><strong>Roll Holder :</strong> 300mm</li><li>Start Photocell</li><li>Mechanical Unwinder</li><li>End of Roll Alarm</li><li>Label Present onto Pad Applicator</li><li>Anodised aluminium and stainless steel construction</li><li>Label roll unwind unit for reels up to 300mm O/D</li><li>Application &#8211; vacuum transfer pad on pneumatic arm</li><li>Variable dispensing speed control</li></ul>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c8333b0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="c8333b0" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/OpLT0tRJW4Y" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
