					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-53d3f08c" data-id="53d3f08c" data-element_type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-35d1c8be elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="35d1c8be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Panda JR</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-431ec72c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="431ec72c" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u648355-5">The Panda Print and Apply Label Applicator is designed to automatically print and apply self-adhesive labels in real time efficiently and reliably. It is well proven in a variety of variable data printing applications, including logistics and tote labelling, to primary product ready meals and fresh produce labelling. Thanks to its incredibly robust design the Panda is capable of operating in the harshest industrial environments.</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Specification</strong></span></p>
<ul id="u655536-16" class="list0 nls-None">
<li id="u655536-3"><strong><span id="u655536">Electronic Control:</span></strong>&nbsp;ER</li>
<li id="u655536-6"><strong><span id="u655536-4">Display:</span></strong>&nbsp;4 LED &#8211; Function Keys</li>
<li id="u655536-9"><strong><span id="u655536-7">Print Engine:</span></strong>&nbsp;Sato® LT408 &#8211; 4&#8243; (105mm)</li>
<li id="u655536-12"><strong><span id="u655536-10">Applicator Unit:</span></strong>&nbsp;Pneumatic Linear</li>
<li id="u655536-15"><span id="u655536-13"><strong>Roll Holder:</strong>&nbsp;</span>300mm</li>
<li>Start Photocell</li>
<li>Mechanical Unwinder</li>
<li>End of Roll Alarm</li>
<li>Label Present onto Pad Applicator</li>
<li>Anodised aluminium and stainless steel construction</li>
<li>Label roll unwind unit for reels up to 300mm o/d</li>
<li>Application &#8211; vacuum transfer pad on pneumatic arm</li>
<li>Variable dispensing speed control</li>
</ul>
<div id="u655538-11" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U655538" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u655538-11_content">&nbsp;</div>
<div id="u658347-12" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U658347" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u658347-12_content">&nbsp;</div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-18feb09e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="18feb09e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
