				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e06c9e2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="e06c9e2" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Panda AL</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ee79ef6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ee79ef6" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>The Panda Print and Apply Label Applicator is designed to automatically print and apply self-adhesive labels in real time efficiently and reliably. It is well proven in a variety of variable data printing applications, including logistics and tote labelling, to primary product ready meals and fresh produce labelling. Thanks to its incredibly robust design the Panda is capable of operating in the harshest industrial environments.</p>
<p><strong>Specification</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Electronic Control :</strong>&nbsp;PLC Panasonic</li>
<li><strong>Display :</strong>&nbsp;Touch Screen</li>
<li><strong>Print Engine :</strong>&nbsp;4&#8243; (105mm)</li>
<li><strong>Applicator Unit :</strong> Pneumatic Linear</li>
<li><strong>Stroke :</strong> 300mm</li>
<li><strong>Applicator Pad :&nbsp;</strong>100mm x 150mm</li>
<li><strong>Roll Holder :&nbsp;</strong>300mm</li>
<li><strong>Rewinding Unit :&nbsp;</strong>Motorised</li>
</ul>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-958e7f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="958e7f3" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/dBRRwiT-AfQ" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
