				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Panda AL</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5543cb2c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="5543cb2c" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u648355-5">The Panda Print and Apply Label Applicator is designed to automatically print and apply self-adhesive labels in real time efficiently and reliably. It is well proven in a variety of variable data printing applications, including logistics and tote labelling, to primary product ready meals and fresh produce labelling. Thanks to its incredibly robust design the Panda is capable of operating in the harshest industrial environments.</p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Specification</strong></span></p>
<div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content">
<ul id="u655448-24" class="list0 nls-None">
<li id="u655448-3"><strong>Electronic Control:</strong>&nbsp;<span id="u655448-2">PLC Panasonic</span></li>
<li id="u655448-6"><strong>Display:</strong>&nbsp;<span id="u655448-5">Touch Screen</span></li>
<li id="u655448-8"><strong>Print Engine:</strong> 4&#8243; (105mm)</li>
<li id="u655448-11"><strong>Applicator Unit:</strong>&nbsp;<span id="u655448-10">Pneumatic Linear</span></li>
<li id="u655448-14"><strong>Stroke:</strong>&nbsp;<span id="u655448-13">300mm</span></li>
<li id="u655448-17"><strong><span id="u655448-15">Applicator Pad:</span></strong>&nbsp;100mm x 150mm</li>
<li id="u655448-20"><strong><span id="u655448-18">Roll Holder:</span></strong>&nbsp;300mm</li>
<li id="u655448-23"><strong><span id="u655448-21">Rewinding Unit:</span></strong>&nbsp;Motorised</li>
</ul>
</div>								</div>
				</div>
