				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c45b90d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="c45b90d" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Bottle-Matic</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2721a74 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="2721a74" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u648397-2">The Bottle-Matic semi-automatic bottle labelling machine applies front and back bottle labels to a multitude of cylindrical objects. Labels up to 380mm wide can be applied onto containers ranging from 12mm to 250mm in diameter at speeds of up to 1000 pieces per hour.</p><p id="u648397-5">Operation is simple – simply set the required label spacing using the index button, insert your bottle/container and press the supplied foot-switch. Upon activation the foot-switch initiates the labelling process and the bottle labels are applied accurately and quickly. With the Bottle-Matic  labelling machine most sized bottles are labelled in less than five seconds.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><ul><li>Applies bottles up to 380mm wide</li><li>Applies up to 1000 bottle labels per hour</li><li id="u648392-6">Adjustable label spacing up to 265mm</li><li id="u648392-8">Adjustable pressure arm</li><li>Handles tapered containers</li><li>Laser-cut steel side frames</li><li>Aluminium Dispensing Table</li><li>Micro-Switch activation</li></ul>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-aa35f89 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="aa35f89" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/N-eOS6x2iYA" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-66694fa elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="66694fa" data-element_type="section">
