						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2978d10 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="2978d10" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Bottle-Matic</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6058749a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6058749a" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u648397-2">The Bottle-Matic semi-automatic bottle labelling machine applies front and back bottle labels to a multitude of cylindrical objects. Labels up to 380mm wide can be applied onto containers ranging from 12mm to 250mm in diameter at speeds of up to 1000 pieces per hour.</p><p id="u648397-5">Operation is simple &#8211; simply set the required label spacing using the index button, insert your bottle/container and press the supplied foot-switch. Upon activation the foot-switch initiates the labelling process and the bottle labels are applied accurately and quickly. With the Bottle-Matic labelling machine most sized bottles are labelled in less than five seconds.</p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Specification</strong></span></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><div id="u648392-11" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U648392" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u648392-11_content"><ul id="u648392-9" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u648392-2">Applies bottle labels up to 380mm wide</li><li id="u648392-4">Applies up to 1000 bottle labels per hour</li><li id="u648392-6">Adjustable label spacing up to 265mm</li><li id="u648392-8">Adjustable pressure arm</li><li>Handles tapered containers</li><li>Laser-cut steel side frames</li><li>Aluminium Dispensing Table</li><li>Micro-Switch activation</li></ul></div><div id="u648393-11" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U648393" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u648393-11_content"> </div></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ae92e63 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="ae92e63" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/N-eOS6x2iYA" target="_blank">
