				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0b114a4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="0b114a4" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">X-Sticker TR</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8317924 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="8317924" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u648424-2">The Label X Sticker is a stand-alone label applicator specially designed as a low cost solution for applying self-adhesive labels to cylindrical containers. It is driven by a stepper motor for superior reliability to improve workflow and minimise production downtime. This sturdy label applicator has been built to withstand heavy use within harsh environments, and is principally constructed of treated steel for high resistance against corrosion and wear.</p><p id="u648424-5">This state of the art machine is able to dispense labels at variable speeds of up to 20 meters per minute and by adjusting the on board controls the X Sticker is able to apply labels to containers ranging from 30mm to 100mm in diameter.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">Stepper motor drive</li><li id="u633640-4">Applicator mounted controls</li><li id="u633640-6">Speed and dwell times</li><li id="u633640-8">Label roll unwind unit for reels up to 250mm o/d</li><li id="u633640-10">Left or right hand versions available</li><li id="u633640-12">Variable dispensing speed up to 20 m/min</li><li id="u633640-14">On board controls</li><li>140mm web width</li><li>Can handle bottles up to 100mm in diameter</li><li>Ready to plug in and use immediately</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1aaaa92 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="1aaaa92" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/IoTyLN7F6j0" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
