				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9579a74 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="9579a74" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Label X JR TR</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9b9a6e5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="9b9a6e5" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u648355-2">The Label X JR TR is a compact, economic and reliable Semi-Automatic Applicator for self adhesive bottle labels. It is adjustable for cylindrical containers from 30mm diameter to 120mm diameter and can apply bottle labels up to 200mm x 350mm in size. Its microprocessor controlled, stepper motor driven labelling head ensures accuracy and reliability. Bottles are fed into the machine by hand and the operator pulls a lever which initiates the labelling cycle.</p><p id="u648355-5"> The Label X JR TR Bottle Labelling machine can accommodate a full roll of bottle labels up to 300mm in diameter and the waste take up spool can accommodate the waste backing paper from a full roll of bottle labels. This outstanding labeller is frame mounted and ready to integrate into any existing workflow.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">Stepper motor drive</li><li id="u633640-4">Microprocessor Controlled</li><li id="u633640-6">On-board control for adjustments</li><li id="u633640-8">Label Roll unwind unit</li><li id="u633640-10">140mm and 200mm Web Widths available</li><li id="u633640-12">Max Label length 350mm</li><li id="u633640-14">Can accept 44mm or 76mm cores</li><li>Adjustable dispensing speed</li><li>Can accept containers up to 120mm</li><li>Handwheel adjustment for label position</li><li>Fixed supports in anodized aluminium</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-097f320 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="097f320" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/CC9XHVr5mg8" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-6bc2c46 elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="6bc2c46" data-element_type="section">
