				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f125336 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="f125336" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Label X JR Compact WR</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ee72972 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ee72972" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u633589-2">Specifically designed for wraparound labelling applications on small cylindrical products such as vials and test tubes the Label X JR Compact WR Automatic Labelling machine can label up to 3600 products per hour. Featuring a built-in end of roll and missing label alarm which alerts the operator to the issue, keeping your production running smoothly.</p><p id="u633589-5">The Compact WR label applicator can accept a maximum label width of 140mm to 250mm and can retain up to 30 different label formats in its externally mounted control box. The dual push-pull transport mechanism ensures accurate and reliable label application to your products.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">Label X JR 140mm or 250mm Labelling Head</li><li id="u633640-4">EW Externally Mounted Electronic Control Box</li><li id="u633640-6">Max Label Width – 140mm or 250mm</li><li id="u633640-8">Electronic Adjustment for label dwell time</li><li id="u633640-10">Missing Label On Reel compensator</li><li id="u633640-12">Labels Applied counter</li><li id="u633640-14">Retained Memory of up to 30 label formats</li><li>300m Diameter Full Spool Unwinder</li><li>End of Roll Label Alarm</li><li>Stepper Motor Drive</li><li>Dual drive push-pull label transport mechanism</li><li>Label Dispensing Beak Adjustable 0-90º</li><li>Stop and Start Photocells</li><li>Handwheels for precise X-Y label positioning</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7d133ec elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="7d133ec" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
