				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6362643 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="6362643" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Label X JR Compact WX</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-832a234 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="832a234" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u633499-2">The Label X JR Compact WX uses a stepper motor drive combined with a dual drive push and pull label transport mechanism to perfectly apply wraparound labels to bottle or other cylindrical products.</p><p id="u633499-5">The Label X JR Compact WX automatic label applicator has a max label width of 140mm – 250mm meaning it is perfect for bottles or other cylindrical products that require wraparound labels. With built in features such as the end of roll alarm to notify the operator of when the machine has stopped the Label X JR Compact WX helps save on downtime and increases efficiency within the workplace. It is also incredibly versatile with a built in memory for up to 30 different label formats which can be programmed in via the externally mounted control box giving the operator complete control for precision labelling.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">Label X JR 140mm or 250mm Labelling Head</li><li id="u633640-4">EW Externally Mounted Electronic Control Box</li><li id="u633640-6">Max Label Width – 140mm or 250mm</li><li id="u633640-8">Electronic Adjustment for label dwell time</li><li id="u633640-10">Missing Label On Reel compensator</li><li id="u633640-12">Labels Applied counter</li><li id="u633640-14">Retained Memory of up to 30 label formats</li><li>300m Diameter Full Spool Unwinder</li><li>End of Roll Label Alarm</li><li>Stepper Motor Drive</li><li>Dual drive push-pull label transport mechanism</li><li>Label Dispensing Beak Adjustable 0-90º</li><li>Stop and Start Photocells</li><li>Handwheels for precise X-Y label positioning</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c613024 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="c613024" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/HrMxtqpk1Mg" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
