				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d0593da elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="d0593da" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Label X JR Compact WA</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e6470ad elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="e6470ad" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u633527-2">The Label X JR Compact WA Label Applicator is designed for Medium to High Volume and is capable of labelling a maximum 3600 products per hour.</p><p id="u633527-5">Manufactured for cylindrical products that requires wraparound labels that adhere perfectly, the Label X JR Compact WA offers an excellent range of flexibility, accuracy and speed. The Label X JR can accept labels ranging from 140mm to 250mm making perfect for bottles, jars and other types of cylindrical product containers. Boasting an end of label and missing label alarm the Label X JR Compact WA can help save on downtime by alerting operators to the machine stopping helping your business meet those all-important deadlines. The Dual push and pull label transport mechanism ensures the perfect placement and adherence of the label to the product every-time.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">Label X JR 140mm or 250mm Labelling Head</li><li id="u633640-4">EW Externally Mounted Electronic Control Box</li><li id="u633640-6">Max Label Width – 140mm or 250mm</li><li id="u633640-8">Electronic Adjustment for label dwell time</li><li id="u633640-10">Missing Label On Reel compensator</li><li id="u633640-12">Labels Applied counter</li><li id="u633640-14">Retained Memory of up to 30 label formats</li><li>300m Diameter Full Spool Unwinder</li><li>End of Roll Label Alarm</li><li>Stepper Motor Drive</li><li>Dual drive push-pull label transport mechanism</li><li>Label Dispensing Beak Adjustable 0-90º</li><li>Stop and Start Photocells</li><li>Handwheels for precise X-Y label positioning</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5890d5b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="5890d5b" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/BtvKvfu5LnA" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
