				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ae106f9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="ae106f9" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Label X JR Compact TB</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-93eb1d4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="93eb1d4" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u633605-2">The Label X JR Compact TB Automatic Labelling Machine is a robust and reliable machine for applying labels to both the top and bottom surfaces of flat products. Designed for High Volume Labelling at Low to Medium speeds the Label X JR Compact TB Automatic Label Applicator is capable of labelling a maximum 3600 products per hour.</p><p id="u633605-5">Manufactured for products with a flat surface that require labels to adhere perfectly to the top and bottom of the packaging, the Label X JR Compact TB Automatic Labelling Machine offers an excellent range of flexibility, accuracy and speed. The Label X JR Compact TB can accept labels ranging from 140mm to 250mm making it perfect for a wide range of products with a flat surface that require labelling.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">2 x Label X JR 140mm or 250mm Labelling Head</li><li id="u633640-4">EW Externally Mounted Electronic Control Box</li><li id="u633640-6">Max Label Width – 140mm or 250mm</li><li id="u633640-8">Electronic Adjustment for label dwell time</li><li id="u633640-10">Missing Label On Reel compensator</li><li id="u633640-12">Labels Applied counter</li><li id="u633640-14">Retained Memory of up to 30 label formats</li><li>300m Diameter Full Spool Unwinder</li><li>End of Roll Label Alarm</li><li>Stepper Motor Drive</li><li>Dual drive push-pull label transport mechanism</li><li>Label Dispensing Beak Adjustable 0-90º</li><li>Stop and Start Photocells</li><li>Handwheels for precise X-Y label positioning</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d4b401d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="d4b401d" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/n6XpJagoSwk" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-926688b elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="926688b" data-element_type="section">
