						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3658e9d5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="3658e9d5" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Label X JR Compact TB</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-52886c1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="52886c1e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u633605-2">The Label X JR Compact TB Automatic Labelling Machine is a robust and reliable machine for applying labels to both the top and bottom surfaces of flat products. Designed for High Volume Labelling at Low to Medium speeds the Label X JR Compact TB Automatic Label Applicator is capable of labelling a maximum 3600 products per hour.</p><p id="u633605-5">Manufactured for products with a flat surface that require labels to adhere perfectly to the top and bottom of the packaging, the Label X JR Compact TB Automatic Labelling Machine offers an excellent range of flexibility, accuracy and speed. The Label X JR Compact TB can accept labels ranging from 140mm to 250mm making it perfect for a wide range of products with a flat surface that require labelling.</p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Specification</strong></span></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">2 x Label X JR 140mm or 250mm Labelling Head</li><li id="u633640-4">EW Externally Mounted Electronic Control Box</li><li id="u633640-6">Max Label Width &#8211; 140mm or 250mm</li><li id="u633640-8">Electronic Adjustment for label dwell time</li><li id="u633640-10">Missing Label On Reel compensator</li><li id="u633640-12">Labels Applied counter</li><li id="u633640-14">Retained Memory of up to 30 label formats</li><li>300m Diameter Full Spool Unwinder</li><li>End of Roll Label Alarm</li><li>Stepper Motor Drive</li><li>Dual drive push-pull label transport mechanism</li><li>Label Dispensing Beak Adjustable 0-90º</li><li>Stop and Start Photocells</li><li>Handwheels for precise X-Y label positioning</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-10b31112 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="10b31112" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
