				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-44f31e8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="44f31e8" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Label X JR Compact TS</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-93f5afd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="93f5afd" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p id="u633638-2">The Label X JR Compact TS Automatic Labelling Machine is specialised to accurately and reliable apply labels to the top surfaces of flat products. Designed for High Volume Labelling at Low to Medium speeds the Label X JR Compact TS Automatic Label Applicator is capable of labelling a maximum 3600 products per hour. This machine also features an end of roll and missing label alarm which alerts the operator to the problem, to keep your operation running smoothly and efficiently.</p><p id="u633638-5">The Compact TS is manufactured for products with a flat surface that require labels to adhere perfectly to the top of the packaging and boasts unrivalled precision in addition to flexibility, accuracy and speed. The Label X JR Compact TS can accept labels ranging from 140mm to 250mm making it perfect for a wide range of products with a flat surface that require labelling.</p><p><strong>Specification</strong></p><div id="u633640-17" class="clearfix grpelem shared_content" data-muse-uid="U633640" data-muse-type="txt_frame" data-ibe-flags="txtStyleSrc" data-content-guid="u633640-17_content"><ul id="u633640-15" class="list0 nls-None"><li id="u633640-2">Label X JR 140mm or 250mm Labelling Head</li><li id="u633640-4">EW Externally Mounted Electronic Control Box</li><li id="u633640-6">Max Label Width – 140mm or 250mm</li><li id="u633640-8">Electronic Adjustment for label dwell time</li><li id="u633640-10">Missing Label On Reel compensator</li><li id="u633640-12">Labels Applied counter</li><li id="u633640-14">Retained Memory of up to 30 label formats</li><li>300m Diameter Full Spool Unwinder</li><li>End of Roll Label Alarm</li><li>Stepper Motor Drive</li><li>Dual drive push-pull label transport mechanism</li><li>Label Dispensing Beak Adjustable 0-90º</li><li>Stop and Start Photocells</li><li>Handwheels for precise X-Y label positioning</li></ul></div>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-98430c9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="98430c9" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																<a href="https://youtu.be/w5XdMd9ufwA" target="_blank">
							<img loading="lazy" width="300" height="50" src="https://etiquette.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/view-video-button-1-1-1.png" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-2161" alt="" />								</a>
															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
